{
  "title": "Malty Syrian Pistachio Pilaf",
  "description": "A malty, springy Syrian dish featuring pistachio, perfect for a hangover cure. This kosher-friendly pilaf is made in a wok and includes ferment-jang for added flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
